{"id": 4678, "title": "Ticket #4678: macro_expand() ignores default param values", "description": "<blockquote>\nmacro_expand() expands macros in a string, but ignores the param defaults table. Thus, a lookup of \"$(LIBEXEC)/condor_history_helper\" results in \"/condor_history_helper\" when LIBEXEC is only defined in the defaults table.\n\n<p>There are two visible errors from this behavior:\n</p><ul>\n<li>Shared port doesn't work on Mac OS X when DAEMON_SOCKET_DIR=auto and LOCK is only defined in the defaults table. (only in 8.3.1)\n</li><li>Remote condor_history doesn't work when LIBEXEC is only defined in the defaults table. (In 8.1.2 and beyond)\n</li></ul>\n\n<p>The function can easily be fixed to use the defaults table and recognize subsystem-specific settings. Also, some callers of macro_expand() need to be changed to free the returned string.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2014-Nov-06 09:49:39 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\nCODE REVIEW: change looks good.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Nov-19 14:41</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/9ff8f6d51a7b24e12027776fe7c1086f641ff437\">[41688]</a></span>: minor 8.3.2 version history item edit <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4678\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4678'); return false;\" title=\"macro_expand() ignores default param values\">#4678</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Nov-04 10:44</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/d660767b7fe5188ccc6c3dc17cd1a89fe45364e9\">[41570]</a></span>: minor 8.2.4 version history item edits for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4678\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4678'); return false;\" title=\"macro_expand() ignores default param values\">#4678</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4680\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4680'); return false;\" title=\"condor_gangliad always logs using gmetric on reconfig\">#4680</a></span>, and <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4557\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4557'); return false;\" title=\"HTCondor-C should gracefully handle authentication issues\">#4557</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Oct-24 16:42</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/9d54f9d6844a7428bd1a81afff48665da2fd275b\">[41447]</a></span>: Docs for shared port on Mac bug fix. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4678\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4678'); return false;\" title=\"macro_expand() ignores default param values\">#4678</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Oct-24 16:41</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/17017740fa76c12b23ddba84d2d587e11d429be5\">[41446]</a></span>: Fix a minor memory leak in the sha